<div class="container">
    <h1>Details</h1>
    <h3>Business Policies</h3>
    <p>At ShipBase, our goal is to provide our customers with the best possible shopping experience for computer peripherals. We are committed to providing high-quality products at competitive prices and delivering excellent customer service. </p>
    <h3>Shipping Policy and Rates</h3>
    <p>We offer free standard shipping on all orders over $50. For orders under $50, we offer fixed-rate shipping of 10% of the order price before tax. Orders typically ship within 1-2 business days and delivery time will vary based on location. </p>
    <h3>Tax Policy</h3>
    <p>ShipBase is required to collect sales tax on orders shipped to certain states based on local tax laws. The tax rate applied to your order will generally be the combined state and local rate for the location where your order is being shipped. </p>
    <h3>Return Policy</h3>
    <p>We want our customers to be completely satisfied with their purchase from ShipBase. If you are not satisfied with your order for any reason, we offer a hassle-free return policy. Items can be returned within 30 days of purchase for a refund or exchange. All returned items must be in their original condition and packaging. Shipping fees are non-refundable, and the customer is responsible for return shipping costs. </p>
